g.text: The diamond's fallback function iterates through a
mapping of function selectors to the address of the
facet containing the function, to find a match.
2 : Check if diamond has caller function
3 : Return result if diamond has caller function
4 : If no caller function in diamond, call the fallback function
5 : Notify if caller function doesn't exist
6 : Delegate call to corresponding facet if caller function is listed
